content:
Predictions for the rest of 2016:

Australia elects a crocodile as Prime Minister after it eats an illegal immigrant in Cairns.
Trump's 1st presidential meeting with Trudeau ends badly after Trump says Canadians are "just snow Mexicans". The next day Canada is nuked.
In a global referendum, humans vote to accelerate climate change because it will hurt Muslim countries first.
France's Front National win everything (including France Has Got Talent) and ban all brown people from France. Nobody even notices anymore.
Literally every creative person left dies. Except Gary Glitter who releases a new album.
Anders Brevik is freed from prison after large crowds protest that he just had "genuine concerns".
Aliens announce war on earth. Earth gratefully accepts its demise.
